  "privacyPolicyIntro": "Cocotte Minute respects your data. Here is, simply put, what the app collects and why.",
  "privacyPolicyS1Title": "What we collect",
  "privacyPolicyS1Body": "Your recipes, folders, tags, people and shopping lists, plus your account email if you created one. As a guest, only an anonymous technical identifier is used.",
  "privacyPolicyS2Title": "Why we use it",
  "privacyPolicyS2Body": "Only to make the app work: saving your content, syncing it across your devices and generating your shopping lists. No data resale, no targeted advertising.",
  "privacyPolicyS3Title": "Where it is stored",
  "privacyPolicyS3Body": "On secure servers hosted in the European Union. Your shopping lists are also kept on your device to work offline.",
  "privacyPolicyS4Title": "For how long",
  "privacyPolicyS4Body": "As long as your account exists. If you delete your account, your data is anonymised immediately then permanently erased within 30 days. For a guest account, deletion is immediate.",
  "privacyPolicyS5Title": "Your rights",
  "privacyPolicyS5Body": "You can view, correct or delete your data at any time from the app (Account → Manage my data). For any question, write to us via \"Contact us\".",

  "termsIntro": "By using Cocotte Minute, you agree to these few common-sense rules.",
  "termsS1Title": "The service",
  "termsS1Body": "Cocotte Minute lets you create, organise and cook your recipes, and generate shopping lists. The service evolves regularly; some features may change.",
  "termsS2Title": "Your content",
  "termsS2Body": "Your recipes belong to you. You simply allow us to store and display them to provide the service — nothing else.",
  "termsS3Title": "Guest account",
  "termsS3Body": "Without an account, your data is tied to this device. Create an account at any time to secure it: everything is kept during the conversion.",
  "termsS4Title": "Acceptable use",
  "termsS4Body": "Don't use the app to publish illegal content or infringe the rights of others, and don't attempt to disrupt the service.",
  "termsS5Title": "Deletion",
  "termsS5Body": "You can delete your account and data at any time from Account → Manage my data.",
  "termsS6Title": "Liability",
  "termsS6Body": "The service is provided \"as is\". We do our best to keep it reliable, without being able to guarantee permanent availability.",

